    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>I find it unusual that you ask to weigh 3 oz of ginger and then measure 1/4 cup, but otherwise, interesting recipe! I love how my hands smell after mincing up all that ginger. They look beautiful and taste even better. I added a half cup of cranberries to the muffins to give them a little bit more texture.</p>
<p>I actually made 5 muffins and a loaf of bread, but I wouldn&#39;t recommend it because it seems like the outside cooks a lot faster than the inside. I&#39;d stick with the muffins.</p>
