    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>AppleyEverAfter, thanks for giving them a go!  To clarify, the weight measurement for the ginger is just to help you when you&#39;re at the grocery store. It&#39;s a rough indication of how much to buy. The 1/4 cup measurement is the more important one.  Sorry for any confusion!</p>
